items.name: integration_key
items.label: Integration Key:
items.tooltip: Required, This integration key comes from Tools4ever and provides access to the integration configured in Skyward. Please reach out to Tools4ever Support for this key.

items.name: entity_id
items.label: Entity ID:
items.tooltip: Required, This is the targeted System Entity for the API Requests

items.name: page_size
items.label: Page Size:
items.tooltip: Size of each response back from the API. It's recommended to not go higher than 10000.

items.name: school_year_id
items.label: School Year ID:
items.tooltip: Optional, Limit the enrollment information to a specific School Year. Reference the District_SchoolYear table for a specific ID

items.name: fiscal_year_id
items.label: Fiscal Year ID:
items.tooltip: Optional, Limit the employment information to a specific Fiscal Year. Reference the District_FiscalYear table for a specific ID
